        <div class="">
            <HeroBanner />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-secondary  md:mx-auto py-12 px-5">
            <h2 class="text-3xl text-white">About Me</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 pt-6">
                I am a Full - Stack Web Developer, I have been working with frontend and backend technologies for 6 years. I have solid knowledge on the backend with PHP and Node.js and on the frontend with Vue.js and React.js and even JQuery.
            </p>
        </div>
